<p>一路一美景，一站一诱惑</p>
<p>最美公路G318川藏线，一生的旅行传奇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200921/0de61b01fe90428baad571e15f9d9077.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">318</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在普通人眼里，只是一组数字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在中南友眼里，这是一条朝圣之路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从成都到拉萨-2140KM</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是所有中南友最初的梦想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是终极的梦想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200921/7459d1f6533d410ba7891aaa6ba8eb3b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一路的美景与风情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让旅行者和摄影师神往</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
